[
  {
    "id": "JOB.28.1",
    "book": "Job",
    "bookNum": 18,
    "bookAbbrev": "JOB",
    "chapter": 28,
    "verse": 1,
    "text": "Surely there is a vein for the silver, and a place for gold {where} they fine {it}. {vein: or, mine}",
    "hash": "7fbc505e6a9bd6ecf9ba0e53e79ab2d0a49f0927bf361743b93b14f69d5d05dc"
  },
  {
    "id": "JOB.28.2",
    "book": "Job",
    "bookNum": 18,
    "bookAbbrev": "JOB",
    "chapter": 28,
    "verse": 2,
    "text": "Iron is taken out of the earth, and brass {is} molten {out of} the stone. {earth: or, dust}",
    "hash": "dffe78927941051e8445be88264e9fd6e3bcb15b13e8c376c1311266f028092d"
  },
  {
    "id": "JOB.28.3",
    "book": "Job",
    "bookNum": 18,
    "bookAbbrev": "JOB",
    "chapter": 28,
    "verse": 3,
    "text": "He setteth an end to darkness, and searcheth out all perfection: the stones of darkness, and the shadow of death.",
    "hash": "a6f6204e6ecdd115ec556ada03cfd65f09812ba64aaa9b9b0e54db7ea5811fb8"
  },
  {
    "id": "JOB.28.4",
    "book": "Job",
    "bookNum": 18,
    "bookAbbrev": "JOB",
    "chapter": 28,
    "verse": 4,
    "text": "The flood breaketh out from the inhabitant; {even the waters} forgotten of the foot: they are dried up, they are gone away from men.",
    "hash": "4fd4911783519b5b08e0d61a58dd9e5a67f4974bb343df95e5e3541d4ad3d32b"
  },
  {
    "id": "JOB.28.5",
    "book": "Job",
    "bookNum": 18,
    "bookAbbrev": "JOB",
    "chapter": 28,
    "verse": 5,
    "text": "{As for} the earth, out of it cometh bread: and under it is turned up as it were fire.",
    "hash": "69f9e6efbfb1ac794e3a5949f7d908cd45599fb5e29f6d3b310c874e949992bd"
  },
  {
    "id": "JOB.28.6",
    "book": "Job",
    "bookNum": 18,
    "bookAbbrev": "JOB",
    "chapter": 28,
    "verse": 6,
    "text": "The stones of it {are} the place of sapphires: and it hath dust of gold. {dust...: or, gold ore}",
    "hash": "24571e5f685da46047c1e702697b7935fd5be410f58a40953414dcd2cb9e0325"
  },
  {
    "id": "JOB.28.7",
    "book": "Job",
    "bookNum": 18,
    "bookAbbrev": "JOB",
    "chapter": 28,
    "verse": 7,
    "text": "{There is} a path which no fowl knoweth, and which the vulture's eye hath not seen:",
    "hash": "2e74a292044c0d911a93f34bea714c091b528a2c1d2b65a276b4f44134b570b9"
  },
  {
    "id": "JOB.28.8",
    "book": "Job",
    "bookNum": 18,
    "bookAbbrev": "JOB",
    "chapter": 28,
    "verse": 8,
    "text": "The lion's whelps have not trodden it, nor the fierce lion passed by it.",
    "hash": "630480733d8293038f64a21035c5d84343865ba89cc2a71456ee7a0b946da8d1"
  },
  {
    "id": "JOB.28.9",
    "book": "Job",
    "bookNum": 18,
    "bookAbbrev": "JOB",
    "chapter": 28,
    "verse": 9,
    "text": "He putteth forth his hand upon the rock; he overturneth the mountains by the roots. {rock: or, flint}",
    "hash": "bf74ee0d7fba78370f195583fae3aae043dde1be0b2fe9497b3ab6be019fd5c0"
  },
  {
    "id": "JOB.28.10",
    "book": "Job",
    "bookNum": 18,
    "bookAbbrev": "JOB",
    "chapter": 28,
    "verse": 10,
    "text": "He cutteth out rivers among the rocks; and his eye seeth every precious thing.",
    "hash": "8a6a9bfbed6d889a7457ba42a6d21f33cb748b65da6653b6c86f4fb203f14586"
  },
  {
    "id": "JOB.28.11",
    "book": "Job",
    "bookNum": 18,
    "bookAbbrev": "JOB",
    "chapter": 28,
    "verse": 11,
    "text": "He bindeth the floods from overflowing; and {the thing that is} hid bringeth he forth to light. {overflowing: Heb. weeping}",
    "hash": "4e3e845e8261aa608729e2c125a119c819c4050ecbb4b563224ce9ea98f7abe0"
  },
  {
    "id": "JOB.28.12",
    "book": "Job",
    "bookNum": 18,
    "bookAbbrev": "JOB",
    "chapter": 28,
    "verse": 12,
    "text": "But where shall wisdom be found? and where {is} the place of understanding?",
    "hash": "9aa89fedbb634240b127c0712f938441812feee5ae0b6abf7c4ca10ce680ad6b"
  },
  {
    "id": "JOB.28.13",
    "book": "Job",
    "bookNum": 18,
    "bookAbbrev": "JOB",
    "chapter": 28,
    "verse": 13,
    "text": "Man knoweth not the price thereof; neither is it found in the land of the living.",
    "hash": "fe5cbfd820036f42cb031f4000fd374ce35067cc952851e67d1e43bb30ff93dd"
  },
  {
    "id": "JOB.28.14",
    "book": "Job",
    "bookNum": 18,
    "bookAbbrev": "JOB",
    "chapter": 28,
    "verse": 14,
    "text": "The depth saith, It {is} not in me: and the sea saith, {It is} not with me.",
    "hash": "cf3c3fe78c85086c11a30b9490f5cee78ef1219b2191de419c052f3ad51e16bd"
  },
  {
    "id": "JOB.28.15",
    "book": "Job",
    "bookNum": 18,
    "bookAbbrev": "JOB",
    "chapter": 28,
    "verse": 15,
    "text": "It cannot be gotten for gold, neither shall silver be weighed {for} the price thereof. {It...: Heb. Fine gold shall not be given for it}",
    "hash": "11e09005cff779fc3f9dd9c5a5c026a35b1e6ddd75db869e7b4d47f651e9f2cb"
  },
  {
    "id": "JOB.28.16",
    "book": "Job",
    "bookNum": 18,
    "bookAbbrev": "JOB",
    "chapter": 28,
    "verse": 16,
    "text": "It cannot be valued with the gold of Ophir, with the precious onyx, or the sapphire.",
    "hash": "cfba75f72f7684bb97b6edc9d752bbcace4cfcc0bb4012e75f05639a63e94925"
  },
  {
    "id": "JOB.28.17",
    "book": "Job",
    "bookNum": 18,
    "bookAbbrev": "JOB",
    "chapter": 28,
    "verse": 17,
    "text": "The gold and the crystal cannot equal it: and the exchange of it {shall not be for} jewels of fine gold. {jewels...: or, vessels of}",
    "hash": "4b30d11f63e98d39cf8785c5966250f42f80ba215b09db96b4d883b4598c503e"
  },
  {
    "id": "JOB.28.18",
    "book": "Job",
    "bookNum": 18,
    "bookAbbrev": "JOB",
    "chapter": 28,
    "verse": 18,
    "text": "No mention shall be made of coral, or of pearls: for the price of wisdom {is} above rubies. {coral: or, Ramoth}",
    "hash": "1f647e06e85e972d2980dc177ffe26db55dba64abef7f450aa0d2593f460483e"
  },
  {
    "id": "JOB.28.19",
    "book": "Job",
    "bookNum": 18,
    "bookAbbrev": "JOB",
    "chapter": 28,
    "verse": 19,
    "text": "The topaz of Ethiopia shall not equal it, neither shall it be valued with pure gold.",
    "hash": "3f69641fe3fd1af198bc95e31ae6d39043f561e7cfd772d10b7bebb6d93c1a16"
  },
  {
    "id": "JOB.28.20",
    "book": "Job",
    "bookNum": 18,
    "bookAbbrev": "JOB",
    "chapter": 28,
    "verse": 20,
    "text": "Whence then cometh wisdom? and where {is} the place of understanding?",
    "hash": "e537458979bcc5101015cdbce781443bf6ad7855ee2ed590deaa222fa6f5e554"
  },
  {
    "id": "JOB.28.21",
    "book": "Job",
    "bookNum": 18,
    "bookAbbrev": "JOB",
    "chapter": 28,
    "verse": 21,
    "text": "Seeing it is hid from the eyes of all living, and kept close from the fowls of the air. {air: or, heaven}",
    "hash": "2f44af00f1db3dc0d58d3e91cd7c42be288a3f605337df8b310658c45fd6c822"
  },
  {
    "id": "JOB.28.22",
    "book": "Job",
    "bookNum": 18,
    "bookAbbrev": "JOB",
    "chapter": 28,
    "verse": 22,
    "text": "Destruction and death say, We have heard the fame thereof with our ears.",
    "hash": "899692997c40bbeb8cf9a84262a00f305f22f8a5171c95d3958952d74de9c097"
  },
  {
    "id": "JOB.28.23",
    "book": "Job",
    "bookNum": 18,
    "bookAbbrev": "JOB",
    "chapter": 28,
    "verse": 23,
    "text": "God understandeth the way thereof, and he knoweth the place thereof.",
    "hash": "3bde5020ffe94c93462dbab70db4dcf7789711e7dfc73ba7f5fe33d302201f70"
  },
  {
    "id": "JOB.28.24",
    "book": "Job",
    "bookNum": 18,
    "bookAbbrev": "JOB",
    "chapter": 28,
    "verse": 24,
    "text": "For he looketh to the ends of the earth, {and} seeth under the whole heaven;",
    "hash": "848e8b163c71e9117a862d8926b6454d205c4befcc8adc987e531a0d411ed7a4"
  },
  {
    "id": "JOB.28.25",
    "book": "Job",
    "bookNum": 18,
    "bookAbbrev": "JOB",
    "chapter": 28,
    "verse": 25,
    "text": "To make the weight for the winds; and he weigheth the waters by measure.",
    "hash": "7dc71848a1fe179390b31db8c4d054ffc52ddd676f1592f143cb5539029d54b2"
  },
  {
    "id": "JOB.28.26",
    "book": "Job",
    "bookNum": 18,
    "bookAbbrev": "JOB",
    "chapter": 28,
    "verse": 26,
    "text": "When he made a decree for the rain, and a way for the lightning of the thunder:",
    "hash": "82333aab407979fdb7ccf4ff976754bab31d8724b42eb101f97923cc24bf9baf"
  },
  {
    "id": "JOB.28.27",
    "book": "Job",
    "bookNum": 18,
    "bookAbbrev": "JOB",
    "chapter": 28,
    "verse": 27,
    "text": "Then did he see it, and declare it; he prepared it, yea, and searched it out. {declare...: or, number it}",
    "hash": "3bbaf4b4d3ea287469ea257b9f4e446fee5e5073648001f005635a5990592846"
  },
  {
    "id": "JOB.28.28",
    "book": "Job",
    "bookNum": 18,
    "bookAbbrev": "JOB",
    "chapter": 28,
    "verse": 28,
    "text": "And unto man he said, Behold, the fear of the Lord, that {is} wisdom; and to depart from evil {is} understanding.",
    "hash": "187465ceb5beda09e0f443aeab887c822c78a14c367e6b3d863995c167546976"
  }
]